{"tid":2010642,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"手足請槍online assignments (大學M1,M2數）","createTime":"2020-05-10T14:08:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-11T16:44:25.000Z","uid":80998,"like":3,"dislike":27,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"f97f86b31746b0c704d1c7c540ff21fd38733215","tid":2010642,"uid":80998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T14:08:09.000Z","msg":"成日出去無上堂 數底差 唔想再retake <br />\n所以想請槍 價錢可以加TG 詳細傾　@kevin0817<br />\n可以Tg搵我附上啲notes 比大家睇下識唔識<br />\n詳細傾 跪求數神大佬幫忙🙏🙇&zwj;♂️<br />\n6條數（5月11號8點夜晚有試卷），5月12號8點夜晚交<br />\n一日時間做<br />\n內容應該好似正常考試（1-2個鐘長嘅試卷）其實如果識計應該一個鐘左右做完<br />\n<br />\n科目係:Quantitative Methods of Business Management <br />\n成個course 有6課<br />\n1.Linear Programming <br />\n2.Sensitivity Analysis <br />\n3.Advanced Linear Programming<br />\n4.Network optimization problem <br />\n5.Project scheduling <br />\n6.Inventory model"},{"pid":"2b173ea766db3d68a2378de1344bceb2d643e964","tid":2010642,"uid":196924,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T14:11:09.000Z","msg":"超越M1 M2範圍喎"},{"pid":"0bed566292e81beedb10133f2565925b12cb17b5","tid":2010642,"uid":80998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2b173ea766db3d68a2378de1344bceb2d643e964","tid":2010642,"uid":196924,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T14:11:09.000Z","msg":"超越M1 M2範圍喎"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T14:13:02.000Z","msg":"師兄識唔識？ 我都唔知 我自己無讀過M1,M2"},{"pid":"5a24c6bf3ce996c6a51d7776cad20aa91f01148f","tid":2010642,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T14:13:24.000Z","msg":"不過你呢啲根本唔係考計數喎<br />\n<br />\n成日時間既話跟住steps慢慢做一定做到"},{"pid":"2223cf0b3e029655f8c02c8dcb1a6cabd33798a4","tid":2010642,"uid":80998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5a24c6bf3ce996c6a51d7776cad20aa91f01148f","tid":2010642,"uid":196924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-10T14:13:24.000Z","msg":"不過你呢啲根本唔係考計數喎<br />\n<br />\n成日時間既話跟住steps慢慢做一定做到"},"citedBy":1,"